item.title: ...need help
item.dc:creator: @viruz_3 viruz 3
item.description:
@viruz_3 wrote:

Place this inside your compile.bat file:

@echo off
title YourServersName Compiler
"C:/Program Files/Java/jdk1.6.0/bin\javac.exe" -cp *.java
pause

See if that helps any
